{"tid":215656,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"外國維修師傅拍片，話PS4易入小強！","createTime":"2017-04-24T14:17:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-24T14:19:00.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2020369c84a5177c267e8f8b9230344666b3a29f","tid":215656,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T14:17:27.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">【PS4變曱甴屋】嚴重起嚟聞得出 陳年世嘉五代一開見小強<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/supplement/20170423/56595316\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fsupplement%2F20170423%2F56595316&d=NZlAC2w8bMplDXSravNUcWxr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=6d7f809b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fsupplement%2F20170423%2F56595316&h=54f03071\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/supplement/20170423/56595316</a></span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170421/large/1492768830_8aab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170421%2Flarge%2F1492768830_8aab.jpg&h=0f84fc43&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\nPS4的散熱位比其他遊戲機位置較低，縫隙也比較大。<br />\n<br />\n外國有維修師傅拍片指 PS4易入曱甴，我們問過有超過20年維修遊戲機經驗的本地師傅Daniel，答案都幾嚇人：「<span style=\"color: red;\">做過統計七成壞底板的遊戲機是因為有曱甴進入機身，牠們的排泄物帶有酸性，留下的污漬會腐蝕電路板<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。</span>」碰巧有客人留下一部Mega Drive世嘉五代維修，我們陪師傅打開，真的出現小強乾屍一隻，並不只有PS4，遊戲機真的易藏曱甴。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170421/large/1492768826_b29c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170421%2Flarge%2F1492768826_b29c.jpg&h=ff7c99f3&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n打開世嘉五代真的驚現曱甴一隻，乾屍看似死了有一段時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\nDaniel指遊戲機一般放在櫃內，背後散熱位又熱又暗很易招惹曱甴小昆蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。而PS4的散熱位縫隙較大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，位置較為貼地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，較易成為曱甴屋也不無道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。師傅說要分辨遊戲機有沒有小強入侵，無需開機，用鼻已能聞到異味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。被小強破壞的電路板維修難度很高，Daniel覺得維修好也不會耐用，一般來說也需要換整塊底板或者整台報銷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170421/large/1492768829_71ed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170421%2Flarge%2F1492768829_71ed.jpg&h=a4713dd8&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\nDaniel形容有曱甴的遊戲機有陣刺鼻的味道，有經驗者自然嗅得出來。<br />\n<br />\n這麼恐怖有沒有預防方法？Daniel覺得打直放會比較安全，另外放在較高和開揚的位置，避開曱甴最愛的死角暗位也是預防方法，不過最重要的還是各位機迷注重家居衛生。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3fExaccW91o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3fExaccW91o&d=NZlAC2w8bMplDXSravNUcWxr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=3f3a31f2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3fExaccW91o</a></div>"},{"pid":"20b16bec3135523828ddce81777209aadafc12fd","tid":215656,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T14:19:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">【PS4變曱甴屋】嚴重起嚟聞得出 陳年世嘉五代一開見小強<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/supplement/20170423/56595316\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%